snippet.title: 'Highly militarized rioters attempt to start civil war in Ukraine'

localized.description:
Kiev mass riots timeline http://on.rt.com/nzmznd

No peace in central Kiev - where despite the reduced number of protesters on the streets the cities embattled center's remained ablaze overnight. Let's get now some more analysis from Graham Phillips, who's a journalist based in Ukraine.
